msgid "BROADCAST Join Hint"
msgstr ""

#: core/analyzers/recommendations.py:565
msgid ""
"When joining with a small table (<200MB), BROADCAST hint eliminates shuffle "
"by sending the small table to all executors."
msgstr ""
"작은 테이블(<200MB)과 JOIN 시, BROADCAST 힌트로 작은 테이블을 모든 executor에 전송하여 shuffle을 "
"제거합니다."

