"alternative root causes, in typical order of likelihood: (1) data-level row "
"explosion from a missing filter or wrong JOIN predicate producing "
"duplicates, (2) duplicate aggregation nodes recomputing the same GROUP BY, "
"(3) key-value skew / heavy hitters / NULL concentration, (4) JOIN key type "
